  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nWhen moving to flat DB we will need an interface that will allow us to separate StateProvider from Trie\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nStateProvider.Get(Keccak stateRoot)\r\n  * main state provider\r\n  * temporary state provider\r\n\r\nIStateStore\r\n * Account Get(Address)\r\n * Set(Address, Account)\r\n * Set(StorageCell, Value)\r\n * Value Get(StorageCell)\r\n * Commit(BlockNumber)\r\n * Dump(TargetStream)\r\n * StateStats CollectStats()\r\n * MoveToStateRoot(StateRoot) // how this works on the flat state? either unsupported or keeps layers, or has some time machine injected that resolves by state root\r\n * StateRoot GetStateRoot()\r\n\r\nPatriciaStateStore : IStateStore\r\nPruningPatriciaStateStore : IStateStore\r\nFlatStateStore : IStateStore\r\n",
